00:23:36.373 --> 00:23:39.293
Kami mahu mendarat di Lapangan Terbang Pyongyang.

335
00:23:39.376 --> 00:23:40.794
Minta maklumat.

336
00:23:40.878 --> 00:23:46.216
Kawalan Pyongyang, Kawalan Pyongyang,
