dan mengalihkan pesawat ke selatan.

368
00:25:47.463 --> 00:25:50.549
Japan Airways 351, Landasan 32, kanan.

369
00:25:50.632 --> 00:25:53.510
Roger, Landasan 32, betul.

370
00:25:53.594 --> 00:25:56.138
Selamat tengah hari, Japan Airways 351.

371
00:25:56.221 --> 00:25:57.514
